
1-go to cart, bring the addItem from cartHelpers.js

2-use it to add the item to the cart

3-find the showAddToCartButton, in the button inside add an onClick property:

onClick = { addToCart };

--add redirect to the state--

const [redirect, setRedirect] = useState(false)


4-create the addToCart function:

const addToCart = () => {
  addItem(product, () => {
    //Add redirect to the state
    setRedirect(true);
  });
};

5-below create the shouldRedirect function 

const shouldRedirect = (redirect) => {
  if (redirect) {
    return <Redirect to="cart" />;
  }
};

6-And call it above the ShowImage component:

{shouldRedirect(redirect)}

--TEST IT --

Go to inspect/application/ clear the localStorate and test it.
